  "original_title": "\u0dbb\u0dcf\u0da2\u0db4\u0d9a\u0dca\u0dc2 \u0da2\u0db1\u0dcf\u0db0\u0dd2\u0db4\u0dad\u0dd2\u0dad\u0dd4\u0db8\u0dcf \u0dc0\u0dd2\u0dc3\u0dd2\u0db1\u0dca \u0d91\u0dc0\u0db1 \u0dbd\u0daf \u0d89\u0dbd\u0dca\u0dbd\u0dcf \u0d85\u0dc3\u0dca\u0dc0\u0dd3\u0db8\u0dda \u0dbd\u0dd2\u0db4\u0dd2\u0dba \u0d9a\u0dad\u0dcf\u0db1\u0dcf\u0dba\u0d9a \u0dc0\u0dd9\u0dad \u0dbd\u0dd0\u0db6\u0dd3 \u0d87\u0dad",
  "text_idx": {
    "en": {
      "title": "The resignation letter sent by President Rajapaksa has been received by the Speaker",
      "author": "unknown",
      "body_lines": [
        "Speaker Mahinda Yapa Abeywardena announced today (July 15) morning that President Gotabhaya Rajapaksa has officially resigned from the presidency.",
        "Calling a news conference, the Kathanayake said, \"I have received the letter of resignation sent by the Honorable President Gotabhaya Rajapaksa in accordance with Article 38.1 (a) of the Constitution. The President has legally resigned from his office effective July 14, 2022.\"",
        "He also mentioned that the constitutional process of electing a new president will be implemented from now on."
      ],
